name: Mastemon
effect:
＜DNA Digivolution: 0 from yellow Lv.5 + purple
                            Lv.5＞ Digivolve unsuspended with the 2 specified
                            Digimon stacked on top of each other. [When
                            Digivolving] Place 1 yellow or purple Digimon card
                            from your trash on top of your security stack face
                            down. When DNA digivolving, you may search your
                            security stack for 1 level 5 or lower Digimon card
                            and play it without paying its memory cost. Then,
                            shuffle your security stack. [All Turns] When you
                            play another Digimon using an effect, delete 1 of
                            your opponent's Digimon whose level is less than or
                            equal to the played Digimon's level.
